div.div:
Creating Server configurations is turned into an activitiy similar to software development where an SDLC determines the outcome and no access to production servers is needed.
Production sysadmin becomes a less privileged activity that has control of how resources are provisioned but does not have the permission to create new configuration types.
Plugins that make it into the repository represent sanctioned configurations that can be activated on domain server resources.
